name: dicom-metadata
title: Code system for dicom-metadata
description:
Dicom metadata defines information on a single dicom image, containing information about the patient, acquisition parameters for the imaging study, parameters for displaying images, and image data.
Code system of DICOM define metadata.
Consist registry of DICOM Data Elements from DICOM PS3.6 2022d - Data Dictionary
